sql: SELECT id, argMax(name, time) AS name, groupArrayInsertAt(0, toUInt32(dateDiff('month', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(count, 2), toUInt32(dateDiff('month', toDate('2015-1-1'), time))) AS commits_count FROM (SELECT toStartOfMonth(created_at) AS time, repo_id AS id, argMax(repo_name, time) AS name, COUNT(arrayJoin(push_commits.message)) AS count FROM gh_events WHERE type = 'PushEvent'  AND (org_id IN [1342004]) AND  created_at >= toDate('2015-1-1') AND created_at < dateAdd(month, 1, toDate('2016-12-1')) GROUP BY id, time) GROUP BY id ORDER BY commits_count[-1] DESC LIMIT 3
